products.title: Carlotti Natural Curtain
products.description: This pale mint green curtain is a beautiful way to bring a subtle touch of class to your windows. Created in a traditional style with a pencil pleat header giving a gorgeous gathered look, this quality cotton curtain will hang beautifully and is decorated with a detailed damask pattern. Not only will the carlotti natural curtain look stunning, but it is also fully lined to provide an effective window covering.

products.title: Alpaca Tamarind Natural Curtain
products.description: Native theme inspired their alpaca tamarind natural curtain is a great way to add character to your home without going too crazy on colour, the soft taupe backdrop is brought to life with the fun styling of the alpacas with small hints or blue and yellow running through there funky accessories. Perfect for playrooms and childrens bedrooms their 100% cotton-based fabric is a suitable and characteristic choice.

products.title: Mr Fish Natural Curtain
products.description: This fun and quirky fish print is both modern and a talk point. Perfect for the fisherman in us all or bathrooms, kids rooms, and kitchens. Mr fish natural is comprised of warm neutral colours, in grey and cream shades, to create this fun oceanic print. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why your curtain comes with a fabulous five year guarantee, for extra peace of mind.

products.title: Cottage Garden Natural Curtain
products.description: Be transported to the garden with this botanical print. Featuring staples of the english traditional garden, this curtain is sure to bring joy to your home. Featuring a blend of soft neautral shades such as browns, greys and creams, this multicoloured, multi-flowered pattern is as beautiful as it is detailed. At swift direct blinds, quality is important to us, which is why your new curtain comes with a fabulous five year guarantee, for extra peace of mind.

products.title: Radiance Pumice Natural Curtain
products.description: This elegant curtain is adorned with beautiful embroidery depicting a bohemian style pattern. The radiance pumice natural curtain is made with a polyester and viscose mix fabric that adds a delicate sheen to the finish. Highly versatile in a neutral beige shade, this fully lined curtain will provide a distinct and luxurious window dressing.
